const handleSubmit = e => {
    e.preventDefault()
}

const SnakeForm = () => {
    return(
        <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
            <label>
            Speed
            <fieldset id="speed">
                <label> Hard
                    <input type="radio" value="100" name="speed" />
                </label>
                <label> Medium
                    <input type="radio" value="300" name="speed" />
                </label>
                <label> Easy
                    <input type="radio" value="500" name="speed" />
                </label>
            </fieldset>
            </label>
        </form>
    )
}
export default SnakeForm;
